			<div id="extension-description">
			<h1>Testmode</h1>
			<p>This component adds testmode functionality to Joomla sites. While offline mode requres users to be 
			logged on to view the site, Test Mode allows you to view the site as a guest would. Also, with the screen door 
			mode you can provide a link to the website which will unlock it to a client so that they can view the site without	
			needing to give out credentials. </p>
